text: Kallnach () is a municipality in the administrative district of Seeland in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. == History == On 1 January 2013, the former municipality of Niederried bei Kallnach merged into the municipality of Kallnach and on 1 January 2019, the former municipality of Golaten merged into the municipality of Kallnach. ==Gallery== File:2012-07-18-Regiono Arbergo (Foto Dietrich Michael Weidmann) 196.JPG|Kallnach File:2012-07-18-Regiono Arbergo (Foto Dietrich Michael Weidmann) 206.JPG|School File:2012-07-18-Regiono Arbergo (Foto Dietrich Michael Weidmann) 201.JPG|Church ==References== ==Other websites== * Official Website * * * Category:Municipalities in Seeland
